Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.66,0:00:02.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉又来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.53,0:00:04.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的一集马上就要开始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.10,0:00:06.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了找齐四魂之玉碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.70,0:00:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了用这把铁碎牙打败奈落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.20,0:00:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桔梗被奈落除掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.34,0:00:12.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈落的分身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.64,0:00:14.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个婴儿\N开始侵袭我们的心灵暗处
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.11,0:00:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偏偏犬夜叉出去找桔梗\N没有办法来救我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.01,0:00:20.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒法师  珊瑚\N七宝跟云母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.68,0:00:22.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿梭于时空\N发生在战国时代与现代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.02,0:00:24.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.25,0:00:31.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分散在蓝蓝天空上的七颗星星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:32.03,0:00:35.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每一颗星星 都刻着我的思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:36.13,0:00:39.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算梦想被粉碎 我也要寻找爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.07,0:00:43.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无处可逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:44.07,0:00:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紧紧抓着我的梦想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.08,0:00:56.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些骗人的光阴 我再也不会输给它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.29,0:01:01.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睁大眼睛 看清楚这瞬间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.79,0:01:05.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它仍然紧紧围绕着我们呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.09,0:01:09.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让人啜泣的 现实生活中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.03,0:01:14.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最重要的…到底是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.24,0:01:17.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繁忙的这个世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.74,0:01:21.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永恒的碎片 忽隐又忽现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.98,0:01:25.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去触摸 去捕捉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.01,0:01:32.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就要循着目标继续向前走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.99,0:01:37.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了得到最后的笑容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.06,0:01:44.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就要循着目标继续向前走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.95,0:02:05.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.66,0:02:08.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我  犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.29,0:02:11.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他急着去找桔梗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.59,0:02:14.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他急着去寻找桔梗的下落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.26,0:02:18.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉不会来救我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.54,0:02:21.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉他…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.84,0:02:22.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于被我找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.07,0:02:28.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于被我找到\N你心灵的暗处了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.38,0:02:32.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧  紧紧的抱着我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.75,0:02:35.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们的灵魂合而为一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.58,0:02:37.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变成我的眼睛吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.92,0:02:44.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.57,0:02:53.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第126话\N将心痛的感觉化为勇气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.81,0:02:58.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送你归西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.64,0:03:00.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们这些家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.22,0:03:09.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既不能置他们于死地\N又要让他们不能动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.58,0:03:11.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只好先让他们骨折了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.75,0:03:14.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来\N还是打妖怪比较轻松一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.32,0:03:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.03,0:03:19.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.89,0:03:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再这么打下去\N太浪费时间了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.30,0:03:24.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇  你千万不能有事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.14,0:03:33.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这两个家伙还活着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.78,0:03:37.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且\N他们也没有意思要那些士兵的命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.31,0:03:41.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这几个家伙\N为什么老是这么笨呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.12,0:03:48.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法师他们迟早会被杀掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.32,0:03:51.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为城里那帮士兵\N还抱着杀掉法师他们的念头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.39,0:03:54.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要把杀人的念头\N传给那些士兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.73,0:03:57.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些凡人马上就会自相残杀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.24,0:04:07.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人的心灵是非常脆弱的\N很容易就会心生憎恨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.41,0:04:10.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个女人也一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.68,0:04:12.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桔梗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.45,0:04:14.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桔梗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.55,0:04:19.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经照着那个老和尚所说的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.92,0:04:22.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算找到这条河附近了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.69,0:04:25.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这一带\N根本没有桔梗的气味
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.20,0:04:31.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且也没有发现过巫女的村民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.40,0:04:35.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎么回事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.34,0:04:38.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个气味是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.94,0:04:40.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.71,0:04:46.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像走掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.22,0:04:51.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好像有点过头了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.29,0:04:55.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不但没有找到犬夜叉那家伙\N而且又跟云母走丢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.46,0:05:00.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看只有用最后一招
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.36,0:05:02.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然除了这个没有其他办法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.10,0:05:07.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么啊  七宝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.24,0:05:11.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想吓死我啊  笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.48,0:05:22.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是云母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.32,0:05:24.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你平安无事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.12,0:05:25.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.05,0:05:28.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇他们\N被带进城堡里面去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.33,0:05:33.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且就在\N我出去找桔梗的这段时间里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.83,0:05:35.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道…又中了圈套
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.63,0:05:39.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是戈薇他们的气味
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.47,0:05:40.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往这边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.34,0:05:43.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,云母  我们快点跟上去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.48,0:05:48.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.58,0:05:49.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定要等等我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.98,0:05:54.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别怕他们  给我射
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.48,0:05:56.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我恐怕不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.65,0:05:58.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.49,0:05:59.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  珊瑚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.02,0:06:03.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在只有发动风穴\N才能保住我们的命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.36,0:06:04.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.59,0:06:07.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一点都不想\N为了活命而滥杀无辜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.93,0:06:09.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这个情况实在是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.43,0:06:10.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放箭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.80,0:06:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一定要尽快进去救出戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.37,0:06:16.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说的没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.54,0:06:19.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么容易就放弃\N根本不是我的个性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.01,0:06:24.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珊瑚  弥勒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.05,0:06:26.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放箭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.02,0:06:32.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.95,0:06:34.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.62,0:06:35.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些混蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.53,0:06:42.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  你这妖怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.40,0:06:44.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是老大吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.77,0:06:47.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们快逃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.07,0:06:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些家伙只不过是人类
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.14,0:06:57.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这股气味  难道是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.98,0:06:58.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.85,0:07:01.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇被他们\N抓进城堡里面去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.22,0:07:02.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.09,0:07:07.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  这是神乐的气味
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.66,0:07:09.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧  弥勒法师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.50,0:07:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是\N告诉我桔梗还活着的和尚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.37,0:07:24.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是个陷阱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.31,0:07:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.01,0:07:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了  来晚一步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.40,0:07:50.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是神无吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.61,0:07:58.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四魂之玉碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.11,0:08:01.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要把这个污秽的\N四魂之玉碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.54,0:08:03.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放入戈薇的体内
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.54,0:08:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇就会完全受我们控制
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.65,0:08:10.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的任务就到此为止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.29,0:08:12.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任务完成后\N接着就要找个地方躲起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.56,0:08:18.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换句话说\N戈薇将成为奈落的手下是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.93,0:08:25.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟琥珀那小子命运相同是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.73,0:08:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琥珀…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.87,0:08:31.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这道污秽的光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.67,0:08:34.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们难道是打算\N把这个碎片放入我的体内吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.51,0:08:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.51,0:08:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体动不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.78,0:08:43.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是这个婴儿\N控制了我的灵魂吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.72,0:08:46.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要摆脱他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.79,0:08:48.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要想办法\N摆脱他的控制
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.02,0:08:51.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  神乐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.49,0:08:54.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个女的很倔强
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.73,0:08:56.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恢复意识了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.17,0:08:59.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快来救我  犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.77,0:09:01.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.04,0:09:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实你心里也很清楚\N犬夜叉不会来救你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.74,0:09:10.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉没有选择你\N他选择了桔梗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.68,0:09:15.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.92,0:09:18.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我简直是个无药可救的笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.79,0:09:22.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧  犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.19,0:09:24.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.69,0:09:25.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.89,0:09:27.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个时候你还在犹豫什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.16,0:09:28.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.30,0:09:29.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桔梗她一定在等着你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.04,0:09:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.98,0:09:43.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又犯了同样的错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.50,0:10:06.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.07,0:10:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以为失去桔梗\N只有我一个人会伤心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.34,0:10:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以没有多加考虑就独自行动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.24,0:10:16.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道这次\N又要失去我最重要的人吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.58,0:10:17.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.88,0:10:19.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等我  戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.25,0:10:21.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答应我你一定要撑下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.45,0:10:23.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你千万不能死啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.45,0:10:27.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好好回想一下  戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.12,0:10:30.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当你听到桔梗死讯的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.99,0:10:33.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实你是很高兴的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.86,0:10:36.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个碍事的女人不在了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.83,0:10:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是后来听说桔梗还没死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.33,0:10:42.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而犬夜叉又跑去桔梗的身边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.97,0:10:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管桔梗是死去还是活着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.34,0:10:48.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉的心始终在她身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.28,0:10:51.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定很怨恨犬夜叉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.65,0:10:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定很憎恨桔梗吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.65,0:10:56.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你恨他们是对的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.88,0:10:59.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件事你根本没有错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.02,0:11:03.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你的心重新充满怨恨吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.19,0:11:05.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我抓住你的灵魂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.90,0:11:11.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平静下来了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.92,0:11:34.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我确实是恨犬夜叉\N我也恨桔梗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.56,0:11:37.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.16,0:11:38.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.20,0:11:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会这样\N碎片居然又被弹了回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.90,0:11:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来你这个小鬼\N也有办不到的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.94,0:11:56.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.58,0:12:00.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个女的开口了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.45,0:12:02.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来我的暗示并没有起作用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.68,0:12:05.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们说的那些\N全部都是错的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.09,0:12:10.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于犬夜叉\N一直忘不了桔梗这件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.96,0:12:12.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我在理智上能够接受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.93,0:12:14.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但还是觉得不甘心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.43,0:12:15.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桔梗…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.10,0:12:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然你们说我恨犬夜叉\N也嫉妒桔梗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.94,0:12:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是只要是人\N都免不了有这样的情绪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.51,0:12:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这并不像你们所说的\N是想诅咒别人的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.35,0:12:34.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直到现在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.25,0:12:37.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉明明知道\N我心里会痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.49,0:12:40.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偏偏还会从我面前消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.26,0:12:44.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是桔梗不在了\N一切都会改观的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.49,0:12:48.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我承认对于会这么想的自己\N让我觉得非常苦恼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.80,0:12:51.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这一切都是因为我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.00,0:12:53.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因为我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.87,0:12:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.64,0:12:58.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我实在太喜欢犬夜叉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.04,0:13:00.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.11,0:13:03.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.05,0:13:06.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.15,0:13:08.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.78,0:13:10.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.39,0:13:14.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的女人\N难怪奈落会讨厌啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.69,0:13:17.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们这些家伙\N把戈薇怎么样了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.66,0:13:22.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只不过\N跟她的灵魂玩一玩罢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.16,0:13:25.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这还多亏了你\N对桔梗一直无法死心的关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.83,0:13:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个女人的心里\N才会出现一线黑暗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.94,0:13:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可惜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.44,0:13:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只差一步\N我就可以破坏她的灵魂呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.64,0:13:38.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们到底想怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.45,0:13:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.55,0:13:42.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.65,0:13:44.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇没事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.32,0:13:45.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神乐  神无
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.09,0:13:48.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛  你们居然还活着啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.69,0:13:53.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法师跟驱魔师\N你们杀了城里多少人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.86,0:13:55.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个婴儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.30,0:13:58.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是这个婴儿\N控制了城里那些士兵吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.07,0:14:00.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你失望了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.33,0:14:02.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从来不会滥杀无辜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.80,0:14:07.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个家伙的模样\N皮肤的颜色淡得这么恶心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.31,0:14:10.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道它是奈落\N利用白灵山那些肉球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.88,0:14:12.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,制造出来的完成型吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.48,0:14:16.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你就是奈落\N那颗凡人的心吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.05,0:14:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会这么认为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.22,0:14:21.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈落那个家伙\N躲在白灵山上的目的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.96,0:14:24.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是为了要制造\N更厉害的肉体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.49,0:14:25.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.96,0:14:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在想他应该也是\N为了扔掉他那颗凡人的心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.26,0:14:30.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且奈落说过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.13,0:14:33.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他已经扔掉\N爱慕桔梗的那颗人类的心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.87,0:14:36.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为他的目的是为了杀桔梗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.87,0:14:38.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说这个小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.61,0:14:41.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是奈落那颗爱慕桔梗的心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.61,0:14:43.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想你一定是弄错了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.71,0:14:47.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个龌龊东西\N只会用肮脏手段来玩弄人心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.88,0:14:51.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.15,0:14:55.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许我真的是\N奈落身上那颗人类的心吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.39,0:14:59.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很清楚人类在想什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.49,0:15:01.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们有弱点而且不堪一击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.76,0:15:04.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很清楚怎么使凡人痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.63,0:15:07.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么使他们悲伤或者怨恨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.77,0:15:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,几乎是了若指掌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.04,0:15:14.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果要问我有什么感情\N是没有从奈落那边继承到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.04,0:15:17.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只有一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.41,0:15:19.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是爱慕桔梗的痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.12,0:15:23.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认为它们会在哪里呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.78,0:15:27.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你们在白灵山上\N看见的一大堆肉球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.79,0:15:29.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那些东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.43,0:15:34.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道那就是被扔掉的心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.03,0:15:39.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我一点都感觉不到\N痛苦跟悲伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.07,0:15:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换句话说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.54,0:15:48.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是奈落日渐扭曲的那颗心\N所变成的怪物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.34,0:15:50.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道这些就够了\N我绝不能再让你留下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.81,0:15:51.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就要你死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.91,0:15:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风之伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.59,0:16:05.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说\N这个小鬼有能力布下结界吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.59,0:16:07.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不可爱的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.70,0:16:12.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风之伤被他吸进去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.51,0:16:19.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了  大家快点逃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.19,0:16:34.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.72,0:16:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个小鬼\N居然可以把风之伤弹回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.23,0:16:44.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别以为游戏就这么结束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.60,0:16:46.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们还会再见面的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.40,0:16:48.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个可恶的妖怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.27,0:16:50.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次你要是再敢碰戈薇的话…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.24,0:16:55.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桔梗死了以后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.64,0:16:59.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在她是世界上唯一能看见\N四魂之玉碎片的女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.98,0:17:01.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.65,0:17:03.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就差那么一点了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.88,0:17:06.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦我们取得戈薇的眼睛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.72,0:17:09.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四魂之玉就大功告成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.46,0:17:12.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是颗充满怨恨的四魂之玉哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.86,0:17:14.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙是笨蛋啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.33,0:17:18.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的以为戈薇会听命于奈落\N乖乖地沦为他的工具吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.23,0:17:22.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对这个女人下手\N以后多的是机会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.44,0:17:24.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.81,0:17:28.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你一天没忘记桔梗\N我就会有机可乘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.18,0:17:37.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.72,0:17:42.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.52,0:17:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很对不起\N我不该抛下你一个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.09,0:17:49.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再也不会\N让你落入奈落的手中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.50,0:17:54.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绝对不会让你\N跟桔梗有同样不幸的遭遇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.38,0:18:10.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了\N没什么精神呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.45,0:18:13.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了  我要稍微睡一觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.22,0:18:18.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到那个戈薇的灵魂\N比想象中还要强大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.66,0:18:20.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,力量使用过度了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.96,0:18:23.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这小鬼在搞什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.96,0:18:26.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道刚刚跟戈薇对峙\N体力消耗太多吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.70,0:18:31.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来就算是奈落的婴儿\N也不是万能的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.05,0:18:46.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偷偷亲你一下\N装作若无其事的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.75,0:18:52.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这样调皮 是不是像个孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.26,0:18:58.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早已习惯 被你说是娇嗔无理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.50,0:19:04.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 「喜欢你」 这三个字\N却始终说不出口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.77,0:19:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My Sweet Emotion
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.18,0:19:19.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对着镜子 多看一次\N看看自己的微笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.75,0:19:32.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果想飞奔出去追求刺激\N就得挺起胸膛向前走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.77,0:19:42.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大胆放手去做 直到满意为止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.48,0:19:52.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偷偷亲你一下\N装作若无其事的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.25,0:19:57.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这样调皮 是不是像个孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.76,0:20:03.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早已习惯 被你说是娇嗔无理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.90,0:20:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 「喜欢你」 这三个字\N却始终说不出口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.27,0:20:12.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My Sweet Emotion
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.58,0:20:25.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枫姥姥  对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.85,0:20:28.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千万别这么说  犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.36,0:20:34.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来就不该强留\N桔梗姐姐在这个人间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.60,0:20:37.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算勉强留在人间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.43,0:20:41.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只会让大姐的灵魂\N继续受苦呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.10,0:20:43.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然这样…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.94,0:20:48.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因为\N我救不了桔梗的灵魂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.54,0:20:51.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才会让她再一次\N落入可恶的奈落手里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.15,0:20:56.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在桔梗姐姐的灵魂消失了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.85,0:20:59.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后她再也不必受苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.15,0:20:59.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.12,0:21:03.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉  你听我说\N你也不必自寻苦恼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.33,0:21:09.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  大姐已经不在了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.63,0:21:10.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.60,0:21:16.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最起码应该\N把她的骨灰还给这块土地吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.64,0:21:25.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇会不会有事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.41,0:21:28.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自从回到村子之后\N她每天都在睡觉耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.22,0:21:31.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧  有犬夜叉照顾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.35,0:21:33.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定不会有事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.33,0:21:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.37,0:21:46.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你醒了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.60,0:21:55.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了\N那天你还是赶来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.44,0:21:58.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.61,0:21:59.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别勉强爬起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.65,0:22:05.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇  当时真的很对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.35,0:22:07.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不应该走开的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.69,0:22:09.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系  我没事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.76,0:22:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会没关系\N那天差点就害死你耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:15.00,0:22:16.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差一点点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.70,0:22:20.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就连现在还活着的你\N也会失去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:23.74,0:22:27.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是\N下次万一又听见桔梗的消息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:27.54,0:22:29.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还是会去找她对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.28,0:22:30.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绝对不会去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:30.48,0:22:32.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后\N我一步都不会再离开你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.88,0:22:33.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你骗人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:34.62,0:22:35.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才没有骗人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:35.75,0:22:37.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明明就是会去的那种人呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.99,0:22:40.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认识你又不是一两天了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:40.72,0:22:42.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你铁定会去找她的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:44.96,0:22:47.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过到时候\N我一样会生你的气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:48.16,0:22:49.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生点气也是应该的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:51.93,0:22:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:59.34,0:23:01.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你果然在生气吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:01.41,0:23:03.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然生气  不过啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.25,0:23:11.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在犬夜叉的心里\N桔梗是不会消失的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.55,0:23:13.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:14.15,0:23:16.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是喜欢你\N所以有什么办法呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.53,0:23:23.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.53,0:23:24.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:41.22,0:23:45.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本以为回到现代\N可以好好的用功个几天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:45.79,0:23:46.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合唱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.80,0:23:47.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞台剧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.80,0:23:49.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烹饪发表会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:49.46,0:23:51.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那还用说啊  文化祭嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.80,0:23:54.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇\N既然你没有参加筹备工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.30,0:23:56.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有候补的工作就交给你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.47,0:23:58.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次看你的表现咯  戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.21,0:24:00.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万一搞砸了\N我们会找你算帐哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.31,0:24:02.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回 犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:02.84,0:24:05.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能下锅恐怖的妖怪干
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:05.61,0:24:08.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找些战国妖怪来\N搞不好还比较轻松



